(43, 6, 68, 44, 4, 12, 12, 'words of eternal life', 'Connection of Salvation and Eternal Life', 'Both passages emphasize the necessity of Jesus for salvation and eternal life. Peter acknowledges that Jesus has the ''words of eternal life,'' while Acts states there is ''none other name'' for salvation.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 6, 68, 40, 16, 16, 16, 'thou hast the words of eternal life', 'Peter''s Confession of Faith', 'This connection highlights Peter''s recognition of Jesus'' divine authority. Both passages emphasize Peter''s acknowledgment of Jesus as the source of eternal life and the Christ.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
